Strafe looks at the scanner, then to Scattershot, "Should we transform
and ingage?" he said with anticipation in his voice.

Grimlock stood up and clenched his fists. "Yess, looks like we get
action soon." he said, relieved.

Hoist ran up to Pacifix, "Great, what else could go wrong, and it's only
been half an hour on our mission." he says sarcastically, but nicely,
and sighs.
